h CYP450 3A4 inhibitors, particularly potent and moderate inhibitors (e.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/27109/', '', 'Salicylic acid, Selenium Sulfide, Thiabendazole, Nystatin, Ciclopirox, Econazole, Flucytosine, Tioconazole, Tetracycline, Acetylsalicylic acid, Minocycline, More', 'Dextromethorphan, Clofedanol, Benzonatate, Pentoxyverine, Codeine', 1767369485);
